description: Serving the finest All Beef Hot Dogs and other Fine Street Eats such as Chicken Sandwiches, Polish Sausage, Nachos, Walking Taco Salads and others.  Because we have a trailer, many times we can go places that the Big Boy Food Trucks can not physically get into.  We can cater business breakfasts and lunches on your premises, customer/employee appreciation lunches and events.  We also are capable of participating in Food Truck Rallies and Festivals.
name: Harvey's Hot Dogs & Other Fine Street Eats
